### Verificación Sprint 3 - Checklist alineado
### Variables: reemplaza @token, @taxpayerId, @eventId, @observationId, @paymentId, @repairReportId

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = TU_JWT_AQUI
@taxpayerId = UUID_CONTRIBUYENTE
@eventId = UUID_EVENTO
@observationId = UUID_OBSERVACION
@paymentId = UUID_PAGO_O_EVENT_ID
@repairReportId = UUID_REPORTE_REPARO

### ----- EVENTOS (checklist) -----

### POST /taxpayer/event — Crear evento (FINE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/event
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "FINE",
  "date": "2025-03-01T12:00:00.000Z",
  "amount": "100.50",
  "taxpayerId": "{{taxpayerId}}",
  "description": "Multa de prueba Sprint 3"
}

### POST /taxpayer/event — Crear PAYMENT_COMPROMISE (validación de multa)
POST {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/event
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "PAYMENT_COMPROMISE",
  "date": "2025-03-02T10:00:00.000Z",
  "amount": "50",
  "taxpayerId": "{{taxpayerId}}",
  "fineEventId": "{{eventId}}"
}

### GET /taxpayer/events/:taxpayerId — Listar eventos por contribuyente
GET {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/events/{{taxpayerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET /taxpayer/events?type=FINE — Filtrar por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/events?type=FINE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET /taxpayer/events?type=payment — Listar pagos (pendientes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/events?type=payment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PUT /taxpayer/event/:id — Actualizar evento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/event/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": "120",
  "description": "Evento actualizado"
}

### DELETE /taxpayer/event/:id — Eliminar evento
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/event/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----- PAGOS (checklist) -----

### POST /taxpayer/payment — Crear pago (verificar que deuda decrementa)
POST {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/payment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-03-03T14:00:00.000Z",
  "amount": "50",
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "taxpayerId": "{{taxpayerId}}",
  "debt": 100
}

### PUT /taxpayer/payment/:id — Actualizar pago
PUT {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/payment/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-03-04T10:00:00.000Z",
  "amount": "60"
}

### PUT /taxpayer/payment/status/:id — Cambiar estado de pago
PUT {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/payment/status/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "paid"
}

### DELETE /taxpayer/payment/:id — Soft delete de pago
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/payment/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET /taxpayer/pending-payments — Listar pagos pendientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/pending-payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET /taxpayer/pending-payments/:id (opcional)
GET {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/pending-payments/{{taxpayerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----- OBSERVACIONES (checklist) -----

### POST /taxpayer/observation — Crear observación
POST {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/observation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Observación de prueba Sprint 3",
  "date": "2025-03-01T12:00:00.000Z",
  "taxpayerId": "{{taxpayerId}}"
}

### GET /taxpayer/observations/:taxpayerId — Listar observaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/observations/{{taxpayerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PUT /taxpayer/observation/:id — Actualizar observación
PUT {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/observation/{{observationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newDescription": "Descripción actualizada"
}

### DELETE /taxpayer/observation/:id — Eliminar observación
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/observation/{{observationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----- REPORTES DE REPARO (checklist) -----

### POST /taxpayer/repair-report — Subir reporte (taxpayerId en body o en path)
### Con path: POST /taxpayer/repair-report/:taxpayerId y multipart "repairReport"
### Sin path: POST /taxpayer/repair-report con body.taxpayerId + multipart "repairReport"
# Ejemplo con Postman/Insomnia: multipart form, campo repairReport = archivo PDF, campo taxpayerId = {{taxpayerId}}

### PUT /taxpayer/repair-report/:id — Actualizar URL
PUT {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/repair-report/{{repairReportId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pdf_url": "https://bucket.s3.../repair-reports/xxx.pdf"
}

### DELETE /taxpayer/repair-report/:id — Eliminar reporte
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/repair-report/{{repairReportId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ----- Sanidad: sin token = 401 -----
GET {{baseUrl}}/taxpayer/events
# Sin Authorization → 401
